This map contains

36 spawns
custom dead space ambient sounds
custom dead space textures in some areas
variable lighting red to yellow
at 2 minutes and 10 seconds a dead space vacuum turns on and slowly kills any afk's or campers (perfect map when admins arent around)


This also contains a custom skybox by [-B-] which is pretty stunning

perfect for almost any gungame server

Check out the map. you won't be disappointed 

USE YOUR FLASHLIGHT WISELY!!
Have fun!
